1:13:58.026 --> 1:14:00.019
You asked me to find
out that witness' name.

1:14:00.146 --> 1:14:01.136
Is it corliss?

1:14:01.188 --> 1:14:03.067
Dwayne geoffrey corliss. Right.

1:14:03.266 --> 1:14:06.022
He's a low life type. Not much came up.

1:14:06.134 --> 1:14:08.127
But, sometimes he goes by dj.

1:14:08.212 --> 1:14:10.329
