questions for ms. Campo.

1:16:27.536 --> 1:16:28.605
Your witness, mr. Haller.

1:16:28.740 --> 1:16:29.729
Ms. Campo.

1:16:29.779 --> 1:16:32.580
Have you engaged to an attorney?

