- no, wait a minute.

1:17:44.575 --> 1:17:48.490
You just testified that you
had never seen mr. Roulet drive.

1:17:48.688 --> 1:17:51.765
Now you're saying, yes, you did
see mr. Roulet get in his car

1:17:51.933 --> 1:17:53.928
and leave with a
prostitute like yourself?

1:17:54.842 --> 1:17:55.911
Which one is it?

1:17:55.964 --> 1:17:59.849
I saw him get in his car, but i
didn't know what kind of car it was.

1:18:00.042 --> 1:18:02.159
You know the difference between
a maserati and a range rover?

1:18:02.246 --> 1:18:05.160
One is small, one is big, i guess.

1:18:05.363 --> 1:18:06.353
Okay.

1:18:09.604 --> 1:18:11.403
The other women.

1:18:12.638 --> 1:18:14.630
