1:18:44.902 --> 1:18:47.862
so you thought, he could
solve your problems with money?

1:18:47.977 --> 1:18:49.046
- No!
- no?

1:18:49.101 --> 1:18:50.981
Isn't that why you're sitting here?

1:18:51.096 --> 1:18:53.010
Because you zeroed in on him.

1:18:53.096 --> 1:18:54.085
No!

1:18:54.173 --> 1:18:57.087
I mean, yes, but it wasn't like that.

1:18:58.372 --> 1:19:00.365
He attacked me. I swear.

1:19:06.605 --> 1:19:09.566
And... alright, let's
pause that right there.

1:19:11.761 --> 1:19:14.800
Just to confirm... this is you?

1:19:14.962 --> 1:19:15.874
Right, ms. Campo?

1:19:16.001 --> 1:19:16.990
Yes.

1:19:17.165 --> 1:19:18.999
