1:19:20.199 --> 1:19:22.077
My name and address.

1:19:22.321 --> 1:19:23.359
And your price?

1:19:24.443 --> 1:19:26.322
Yes, $400.

1:19:27.433 --> 1:19:28.469
It's a hard line of work.

1:19:28.515 --> 1:19:30.509
Yes, and dangerous.

1:19:30.593 --> 1:19:33.430
In fact, haven't you told
your friends many times...

1:19:33.588 --> 1:19:34.781
that you were looking for a way out?

1:19:35.709 --> 1:19:37.702
I'm not proud of what i do.

1:19:37.787 --> 1:19:38.854
I know.

1:19:38.908 --> 1:19:40.741
And isn't it true...

1:19:40.821 --> 1:19:42.974
and nothing will be
easier to understand...

1:19:45.022 --> 1:19:48.015
that you saw louis roulet
and his money as that way out?

1:19:48.137 --> 1:19:49.332
No! That's not what this is about!

1:19:52.296 --> 1:19:53.411
Are you not listening to me?

1:19:54.583 --> 1:19:56.337
No further questions, your honour.

1:19:56.413 --> 1:19:57.449
Mr. Minton.

1:19:57.701 --> 1:19:59.660
Do you have another witness for us?

1:20:01.733 --> 1:20:02.805
Minton looks worried.

1:20:04.976 --> 1:20:06.808
Not worried enough.

1:20:09.134 --> 1:20:10.124
No.

1:20:10.175 --> 1:20:12.054
The state rests, your honour.

1:20:12.170 --> 1:20:15.164
Then the defense will call
its first witness after lunch.

1:20:17.411 --> 1:20:20.210
Yes, i recognise this knife.

1:20:20.361 --> 1:20:23.481
It's the one that my son has
carried with him for protection.

1:20:23.606 --> 1:20:25.642
For the last 4 years, almost exactly.

1:20:26.597 --> 1:20:28.590
Why would he need protection?

1:20:29.714 --> 1:20:32.710
Realtors alone in the house
are sometimes robbed or...

1:20:33.914 --> 1:20:34.869
hurt?

1:20:34.951 --> 1:20:35.989
Even raped or murdered.

1:20:37.157 --> 1:20:39.994
Has louis ever been
subject to such crime?

1:20:40.318 --> 1:20:41.307
Oh no.

1:20:42.314 --> 1:20:43.385
But he knew someone who was.

1:20:43.438 --> 1:20:46.236
Raped and robbed by a man.

1:20:47.385 --> 1:20:48.502
Louis found her.

1:20:49.548 --> 1:20:50.426
It was terrible.

1:20:51.585 --> 1:20:54.498
So, the first thing he did afterwards,
was getting himself a knife.

1:20:54.786 --> 1:20:56.664
To carry it with him at all times.

1:20:57.819 --> 1:20:58.776
Thank you, ms. Windsor.

1:20:58.943 --> 1:21:00.776
I have no further
questions, your honour.

1:21:01.063 --> 1:21:02.101
Your witness, mr. Minton.

1:21:03.057 --> 1:21:04.048
Ms. Windsor.

1:21:05.141 --> 1:21:09.102
You seemed pretty exact about when it was
your son started carrying around this...

1:21:10.294 --> 1:21:11.284
this weapon.

1:21:11.333 --> 1:21:15.249
- A five inch folding knife.
- yes, i am.

1:21:15.575 --> 1:21:19.411
The incident took
place on june 9th, 2007.

1:21:19.774 --> 1:21:21.606
Was it in the newspapers?

1:21:24.805 --> 1:21:25.921
Do you somehow remember it because...

1:21:26.009 --> 1:21:28.002
the police came to talk to louis?

1:21:28.962 --> 1:21:30.955
No, there was no police investigation.

1:21:31.082 --> 1:21:33.199
Then, how do you
remember the exact date?

1:21:33.284 --> 1:21:36.198
Were you given it before
your testimony here today?

1:21:37.360 --> 1:21:38.397
I remember the date because...

1:21:38.442 --> 1:21:41.276
i'll never forget the
date i was attacked.

1:21:41.599 --> 1:21:43.592
And louis won't forget it either.

1:21:44.594 --> 1:21:46.585
He found me in the house tied up.

1:21:46.840 --> 1:21:48.673
My clothes were ripped.

1:21:52.036 --> 1:21:53.869
It was traumatic for him.

1:22:00.225 --> 1:22:01.215
Mr. Minton?

1:22:01.264 --> 1:22:03.258
Is there anything else you wish to ask?

1:22:07.419 --> 1:22:08.537
No, your honour.

1:22:20.510 --> 1:22:23.312
I've been thinking about
those thousand razors?

1:22:31.830 --> 1:22:32.900
We've hads an offer.

1:22:34.043 --> 1:22:35.956
You spend 6 months in the county jail.

1:22:36.215 --> 1:22:38.206
Like i told you from the beginning.

1:22:38.303 --> 1:22:41.265
No deals, no bargaining, i'm innocent.

1:22:41.396 --> 1:22:44.231
Save it. You make the
call. I don't give a shit.

1:22:44.446 --> 1:22:46.434
- You got my answer.
- yes, i do.

1:22:46.613 --> 1:22:48.446
I'll pass it along.

1:22:48.534 --> 1:22:49.524
You do that.

1:22:49.621 --> 1:22:50.611
Oh, louis.

1:22:52.836 --> 1:22:53.826
Tomorrow...

1:22:55.843 --> 1:22:56.957
i'm putting you on the stand.

1:22:58.977 --> 1:22:59.966
