Hey, earl.

1:23:16.724 --> 1:23:18.794
There's something, i
need you to get for me.

1:23:22.112 --> 1:23:25.027
Your honour, the defense
calls louis ross roulet.

1:23:26.285 --> 1:23:29.325
I knocked uh... she looked
through her side window...

1:23:29.461 --> 1:23:30.451
and saw that it was me.

1:23:30.508 --> 1:23:31.497
